sk.tsystems.forum.entities

Class Comment

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.tsystems.forum.entities.Comment

  • @Entity
public class Comment
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the Entity required for creation of the structure in the database using JPA connection. Class is equivalent to the table in database. Encloses fields that are represented as a columns in this table, instances of the class represent rows in the table in the database.

    karolklescinsky
